Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 雖然是情誼巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的情人節已經到了啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:55.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.79,0:01:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有給小健嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買是買了卻沒有送掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.29,0:02:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果只好自己吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光惠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年試著送給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正關係也已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有希望的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會收下嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健的話一定會很高興地吃掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不知道是什麼含義
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.42,0:02:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這時代還有男人不知道情人節的含義嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年都有告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.17,0:02:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可每年都忘掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.77,0:02:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健對沒興趣的事是不用腦細胞的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.69,0:02:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話光是送給他可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要明確的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 小健
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有靈感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第5節課晚點去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.71,0:02:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我和老師說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2月14號是什麼日子知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.64,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是乾貨之日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.31,0:02:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾貨麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.95,0:03:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾貨也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾貨 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.59,0:03:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小健喜歡啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情敵是乾貨嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎..到了這種季節了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得關於戀愛的願望多起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.21,0:03:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八島大人喜歡巧克力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微烤一下沾味噌吃就特別美味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.73,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在說..巧克力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早說了一定要用水熱融化的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喊一聲「神中」一下子完成不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得友裡惠有了幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.47,0:04:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要作為女中學生而不是神仙去送給他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打倒乾貨哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.09,0:04:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說要做巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾~~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該派的上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請隨便用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祀也到了會做這種有女人味的事的年紀了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.79,0:04:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友裡惠要做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是看著而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.24,0:04:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你..有沒有想送巧克力的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個也沒有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天還很遙遠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年就三年級了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始準備升學考試呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為高中生 又開始上學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也會離開這個城市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.47,0:05:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你 最終還是會回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.76,0:05:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是這裡的繼承人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:06:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 不過我還不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.81,0:06:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣都要找個女婿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且巫子她比我有潛質
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能我會找到想做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.13,0:06:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光惠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.35,0:06:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將來想做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為是主婦的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.59,0:06:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫁給那個表兄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.37,0:06:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主婦也是 其他的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都還沒有定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.73,0:06:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後自己會變成怎樣 連推測都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:36.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專業神仙的話 我家可是很歡迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.00,0:06:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道 但是為了決定這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能有一點勇氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛~~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.51,0:07:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做了巧克力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友裡惠也正值青春呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是要送給誰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:24.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但爸爸和小章也有份的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.78,0:07:28.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~~身為父親真好啊
