Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 像現在這樣繼續下去真的好麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是像這樣煩惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太煩惱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就很想說「拜託了 神仙」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為知道現在的友裡惠是什麼心情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.86,0:18:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.82,0:18:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點話還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後的勇氣必須自己拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.55,0:18:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小祀..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神社的女兒是很厲害的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友裡惠大人~~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.67,0:18:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是貓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小窮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.04,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光惠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會就來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.57,0:18:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.99,0:18:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.98,0:18:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友裡惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.83,0:19:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.82,0:19:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油~~~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.96,0:19:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 因為是神仙的貓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學~~
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.61,0:20:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一橋同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有點..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學！！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.62,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.97,0:21:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.45,0:21:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一橋同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.30,0:21:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的話..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.54,0:22:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.63,0:22:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:14.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼沒發覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:17.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友裡惠 認識麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:22:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.26,0:23:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 友裡惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}恭喜您 要幸福哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.90,0:23:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..這個..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.76,0:24:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.91,0:24:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友裡惠大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.73,0:24:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.68,0:24:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.56,0:24:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.53,0:24:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.92,0:24:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的風
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.36,0:24:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在飛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.92,0:24:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是神仙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.54,0:24:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有強風的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.43,0:24:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在屋頂告白的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.83,0:24:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還真中了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.72,0:24:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.69,0:24:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧 友裡惠
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.12,0:24:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真滋潤啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.12,0:25:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是..友裡惠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.24,0:25:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺順利的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.23,0:25:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.44,0:25:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都興奮成那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.96,0:25:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.34,0:25:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原諒他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真年輕啊~~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.05,0:25:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜啊~~太好了呢~~
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.71,0:25:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友裡惠大人將來會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.42,0:25:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名副其實的只有神仙才知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.07,0:25:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健兒君..
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.54,0:25:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.52,0:25:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說喜歡我..是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.31,0:25:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.91,0:25:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.52,0:26:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友裡惠很奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.45,0:26:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.53,0:26:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.32,0:26:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起會很刺激
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.28,0:26:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為怪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.89,0:26:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.98,0:26:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方我一點也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.21,0:26:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.86,0:26:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後也多關照咯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.79,0:26:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.82,0:27:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖暖呵呵溫溫吞吞的春假
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.32,0:27:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在成為三年級前
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.06,0:28:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈也好神社也好 一起大掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.44,0:28:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的春天和每年的稍有不同
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.79,0:28:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…今年有建兒君…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.57,0:28:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一集是 『看吧 春天來了』
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.40,0:28:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後大家一起 親親
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.36,0:28:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣


